        "subject": "LU-10828 osp: Disconnect export during failure case",
        "message": "LU-10828 osp: Disconnect export during failure case\n\nWhen ptlrpc_connect_import() fails in osp_obd_connect() the already\nconnected export is not disconnected causing a reference to be\nheld in the osp module.  This patch attempts to disconnect the\nexport before returning.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jeremy Filizetti <jeremy.filizetti@gmail.com>\nChange-Id: Ic8d1891ea3a257850c2c2f5b7826b7c865911b30\n"
